│ Change:\nplanContainsAdditionalSimplifications(getPlanFor(BestFactor.Width),  │
│ CostCtx,                                                                      │
│ OrigLoop)\nTo:\nplanContainsAdditionalSimplifications(getPlanFor(BestFactor.W │
│ idth), CostCtx, OrigLoop, BestFactor.Width.isVector())\n\nRationale: This     │
│ ensures vector-only ignored instructions are not suppressed when validating a │
│ scalar VF. For scalar VF, IsVector=false causes skipCostComputation to ignore │
│ VecValuesToIgnore, allowing the function to detect that the VPlan omits       │
│ instructions that the legacy model still costs, thus returning true and       │
